                        <p>And if you cannot do these things, then please, do nothing at all. Just leave me alone. Just for a day. I'll call home and talk about what matters. You can program me again on the twelfth.</p>
<p><I>Jesse Panuccio is a Trinity senior and Duke University Union president. </I></p>

